raw_data.title: IT Analyst 1
raw_data.description: Applies developed skills and knowledge in order to design efficient IT systems, which meet business and technology needs. Under general supervision, performs a variety of assigned tasks including analysis of functional specifications, coordinating developers to build and implement technology solutions, and gathering feedback from end users about system performance. May be called to assist with upgrades, hardware/software installation and technical training, among other things.
